    "## Clean Data: Tidiness issues first , then quality issues\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Fix Tidiness Issues ( Structure Issues)\n",
    "* merge pd_prediction_copy and pd_json_copy tables into pd_achive_copy table by using merge() function\n",
    "* combine rating_numerator and rating_denominator columns into one column by using \"+\" and drop original rating_numerator and rating_denominator column\n",
    "* Join combine \"doggo,floofer, pupper,puppo\" together under \"type\" column using lambda function and replace the value types with proper values .\n",
    "* split date and time into two separate columns\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "2. Fix Quality Issues ( Content Issues)\n",
    "(1). pd_achive_copy:\n",
    "* remove extra contents for urls in source column ( eg: <a href= ) with split()\n",
    "* chop extra contents for timestamp column (+0000) with rstrip()\n",
    "* Under name column, replace \"a/an/the/none\" with none\n",
    "* Erroneous datatypes :\n",
    "convert tweet_id,in_reply_to_status_id, in_reply_to_user_id, retweeted_status_id, retweeted_status_user_id\n",
    "all from float to string;\n",
    "convert 'img_num', 'retweet_count', 'favorite_count'from float to integer\n",
